reviews.review_text: The Matrix... This claims to be a Matrix consisting of 60% SBD to 40% AUD. It sounds more like 99% AUD to 1% SBD (and not even a very good AUD: No Phil!). SInce I don't like AUDs, and figure others may feel the same, I just thought I'd warn ya. The performances are top-notch, I wish there was a "pure" SBD of this one...

Well, to each his own But no, this doesn't sound 99-1 aud. It sounds like a nicely put-together Matrix, which means that if you don't like auds, you probably won't like it. To this aud lover, it gives that just right sense of distance and echo that make a matrix more closely resemble the actual sound in a concert hall than what you get with a sbd.  
  As for the show, you want it.
there is a straight SBD. ...just FYI to the guy who was wishing for one. you can use deadlists.com to search this site more effectively, FYI.
loser This is a mighty fine slow version of loser specifically with nice performances by the Godchauxs'
